Package Settings

| Setting           | Recommended Value                        | Why                                    |
| ----------------- | ---------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Name              | Windows Security Compliance - Full Audit | Clear, descriptive                     |
| Run as            | System                                   | Required for registry/Defender changes |
| 64-bit PowerShell | Yes                                      | Better compatibility                   |
| Signature check   | No                                       | Unless you sign scripts                |
| Schedule          | Daily at 2 AM                            | Off-hours, minimal user impact         
